{"tid":829257,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[左膠好波］撰文罵昂山素姬　緬甸作家被判囚7年","createTime":"2018-09-20T10:16:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-20T15:18:53.000Z","uid":6497,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"a67848455279f848943ea09a37258bfee4c96405","tid":829257,"uid":6497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T10:16:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/international/%E6%92%B0%E6%96%87%E7%BD%B5%E6%98%82%E5%B1%B1%E7%B4%A0%E5%A7%AC-%E7%B7%AC%E7%94%B8%E4%BD%9C%E5%AE%B6%E8%A2%AB%E5%88%A4%E5%9B%9A7%E5%B9%B4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E6%2592%25B0%25E6%2596%2587%25E7%25BD%25B5%25E6%2598%2582%25E5%25B1%25B1%25E7%25B4%25A0%25E5%25A7%25AC-%25E7%25B7%25AC%25E7%2594%25B8%25E4%25BD%259C%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%2588%25A4%25E5%259B%259A7%25E5%25B9%25B4%2F&d=3wKPalFIRmNjt9PP99x%2B5YS5T71%2BpEKm9yZKOKwCwR4%3D&h=19a89284\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E6%2592%25B0%25E6%2596%2587%25E7%25BD%25B5%25E6%2598%2582%25E5%25B1%25B1%25E7%25B4%25A0%25E5%25A7%25AC-%25E7%25B7%25AC%25E7%2594%25B8%25E4%25BD%259C%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%2588%25A4%25E5%259B%259A7%25E5%25B9%25B4%2F&h=cb9a8b2a\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/international/%E6%92%B0%E6%96%87%E7%BD%B5%E6%98%82%E5%B1%B1%E7%B4%A0%E5%A7%AC-%E7%B7%AC%E7%94%B8%E4%BD%9C%E5%AE%B6%E8%A2%AB%E5%88%A4%E5%9B%9A7%E5%B9%B4/</a><br />\n<br />\n緬甸一名國營報章的前專欄作家，在Facebook發帖文後，被指涉嫌辱罵誹謗國務資政昂山素姬，周一（17日）被判煽動罪成，周二被重判入獄七年。<br />\n<br />\n雅敏瑞（Ngar Min Swe）於 1 月 24 日在Facebook，發表有關奧巴馬 2013 年訪問緬甸時，在昂山素姬臉上一吻的評論文篇。《法新社》報道，當年奧巴馬的親暱舉動，引起緬甸保守派民眾不滿，尤其是軍方支持的「聯邦鞏固與發展黨」，雅敏瑞同樣通過社交媒體，向昂山素姬發放具性別歧視意味的攻擊。<br />\n<br />\n在緬甸軍政府年代，專欄作家雅敏瑞曾為國營報章《緬甸環球之光》撰撰寫政治評論，多年來持續批評昂山素姬和其政黨「全國民主聯盟」。<br />\n<br />\n緬甸最大城市仰光的地區法院周二判雅敏瑞入獄七年，以及罰款 10 萬緬甸元（約 496 港元）。法院發言人指，他是因在 Facebook 撰寫對昂山素姬具「侮辱性」的帖文，「令人對她有錯誤印象而被定罪」。雅敏瑞於 12 日在家中被捕，其妻指他認為自己並沒有錯，故未有聘用律師代表，僅在庭上自辯。<br />\n<br />\n緬甸政府近年收緊言論自由及新聞自由，不少批評緬甸政府的媒體和民眾被控以煽動和誹謗，外界指今次事件是另一新例。兩名調查羅興亞屠殺的《路透社》記者，被指泄漏國家機密文件，本月初被緬甸法院判囚 7 年，令國際社會嘩然。"},{"pid":"afd8bb009b4e6232fcb5b936ff7580f6b297dc2d","tid":829257,"uid":75610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T10:17:50.000Z","msg":"前緬甸軍政府都幾撚灰"},{"pid":"29bfbdcc6bce1f9ddd284cd930f4a2486df56be9","tid":829257,"uid":6497,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"afd8bb009b4e6232fcb5b936ff7580f6b297dc2d","tid":829257,"uid":75610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T10:17:50.000Z","msg":"前緬甸軍政府都幾撚灰"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T10:21:16.000Z","msg":"軍政府都冇佢做得咁盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"022a50e9f3f8d8805fdf2b5c9bb1c7dc12a35ea8","tid":829257,"uid":99028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T10:24:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"937ee26087f91f359f59063b0f64968a84d3edb6","tid":829257,"uid":69213,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T10:25:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1cbf4497e5b3860c84e682470bab2813c0a66dd3","tid":829257,"uid":95497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"937ee26087f91f359f59063b0f64968a84d3edb6","tid":829257,"uid":69213,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T10:25:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T10:28:41.000Z","msg":"屎味嘅咖哩 咖哩味嘅屎"},{"pid":"345532a546c39e9652503684d010c2073fcc2270","tid":829257,"uid":108347,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"022a50e9f3f8d8805fdf2b5c9bb1c7dc12a35ea8","tid":829257,"uid":99028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T10:24:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T10:39:24.000Z","msg":"夠有高官出身基層啦，一上位未即刻加入欺壓市民囉"},{"pid":"172b209431eb6bd61b6dff24ed440e15cba32868","tid":829257,"uid":56501,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T10:44:02.000Z